item.title: Still no reason to trust them.
item.description: https://kotaku.com/discord-palantir-peter-thiel-persona-age-verification-2000668951 Because of the controversies around Palantir, Discord is switching to Persona for their "Age verification experiment." As pointed out by @DJevelen, Persona is also linked to Peter Thiel, who is their primary investor. Discord already had a data breach, and lost over 70,000 user's personal data back in 2025. Discord has already lied to us three time minimum. #1 They said they will keep our data, which is being handed over to 3rd party. #2 They said they would delete the data once age has been verified, the former companies are both known to never deleting data. Now they are claiming it will only be held for "Seven Days." #3 They said they don't monitor private servers and chats, yet now they say they are using AI to read your private servers and chats to determine your age. This is about data, control, and money above all else. Removing another layer of anonymity from the internet. Infringing on our rights, the freedom of speech, and the ability speak out against the actions of our and other governments.

item.title: Kay Rose is HOME!!!
item.description:
I posted a couple of weeks ago about the longest resident of the Greater Huntsville Humane Society, Kay Rose, who has been there over a YEAR. And @TrustInButtsMcGee messaged me immediately and said she very much wanted to adopt her! And now, barely two weeks after my initial post, KK is in her forever home!!
Our CEO, Spencer (@AlabamaAnimalRescuer), traveled from Alabama all the way to Colorado to bring her to her new - and forever- mama!
She did SUCH a good job traveling, but is SO happy to finally be home! And she has already fallen in LOVE with her mama! Look at that face tilt into her mama’s hand!!
She has been checking out the whole house, and is already so confident!
She even feels comfortable enough to PLAY!! Spencer just keeps saying, “This is NOT the same cat I’ve seen who has spent over a year in a cage!”
Apparently she is following her mom around EVERYWHERE, not letting her out of her sight! Her mama is trying to take a shower but KK won’t leave her alone!
She’s up on the couch…
And flopping down. My HEART
Rochelle, the marketing director for the GHHS, made this ornament for Kay Rose. She, Spencer, and I have all shed tears on this momentous day. KK’s mom said she anticipates her sleeping in her bed tonight…I can’t wait for the report tomorrow morning!!!
As a side note, happy Valentine’s Day everyone! I brought bestie a bouquet to her restaurant tonight. Gotta show the ones you love how much you care!!
Thank you to everyone out there who spread the word about KK. You all have made the difference in her life!!
